<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>KA NUNNAK, BAWIPA CU THANGTHAT! CH35</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa thangthat tuah u, A ngan bik Pathian, Kannih khamhnak ca ah lam
 tha kha a hun, Khamhnak a tha bik kha a kan pek ca ah, Mei alh le minmei
 in a kan kaipi lai.

[C1]
   Nan... aw ngeih vialte in, Bawipa thangthat u, Mi lungchung muihnak
   kha a run ceuter lai, Amah pen dinnak kha a kau chinchin lai, A sermi
   vial-te nih, A sermi vial-te nih Bawipa an hlorh, Maw ka thlarau
   thangthat tuah.

[V2]
 Thlarau tlaumi sinah, Tlanhnak kha a pek, A sualmi ca thiannak tiva a
 luanter, A khamh ciami vialte kha a kan dawt i, Kan thlacam a ngaih ca,
 Bawipa thangthat u.

[C2]
   Nan... aw ngeih vialte in, Bawipa thangthat u, Mi lungchung muihnak
   kha a run ceuter lai, Amah pen dinnak kha a kau chinchin lai, A sermi
   vial-te nih, A sermi vial-te nih Bawipa an hlorh, Maw ka thlarau
   thangthat tuah.

[V3]
 Bawipa thangthat tuah u, Kan vansan lioah, A zaangfahnak hri nih khan
 a kan tlaih cang, Zumh le ruahchan in a teimi vialte he, Dawtnak ram ah
 tling tein kan i tong lai.

[C3]
   Nan... aw ngeih vialte in, Bawipa thangthat u, Mi lungchung muihnak
   kha a run ceuter lai, Amah pen dinnak kha a kau chinchin lai, A sermi
   vial-te nih, A sermi vial-te nih Bawipa an hlorh, Maw ka thlarau
   thangthat tuah.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
<hymn_number>35</hymn_number>
</song>